Enum Class SvgPathCmd

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<SvgPathCmd>
camzup.core.SvgPathCmd
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<SvgPathCmd>, Constable
public enum SvgPathCmd extends Enum<SvgPathCmd>
Command that describes how to render a shape in the d attribute of a path node in scalable vector graphics (SVG).
